

ElasticSearch Configuration
---------------------------

1.Elasticsearch defaults to using /etc/elasticsearch for runtime configuration.
2.Default ownership root:elasticsearc.
3.Elasticsearch loads its configuration from the /etc/elasticsearch/elasticsearch.yml file by default.

Directory layout of Dabian package.
https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/6.8/deb.html#deb-layout



elastic search background (varify again)
----------------------------------------

./bin/elasticsearch -d -p pid
pid -> sudo service elasticsearch status

./bin/elasticsearch/ -> location /usr/share/elasticsearch/bin


